name: Hawa
desc:
A knowledgeable scholar and doctor.
Less self-preservation than is wise.

name: Leda
desc: A swordswoman from the far west. She's brash, aggressive, and Talib's oldest friend.

name: Red
desc: An enormous Ifreet who constantly finds himself in financial trouble.

name: Talib
desc: A young mercenary commander, who is smarter than he appears but not near as smart as he imagines.

name: Yazid
desc: An cynical elder artilleryman in the chain, trusted by few.

name: Harjot
desc: A skilled soldier with no sense of his own mortality.

name: Azia
desc: An armored Naga. She's kind and softspoken.

name: Jameela
desc: A sincere, honest, and kind gargoyle knight.

name: Tufayl
desc: A skilled smith and perennial party crasher.

name: Kavitha
desc: A seasoned but self-important monster hunter.

name: Muneeb
desc: A new recruit recently given command. He's eager to prove himself.

name: Nasruddin
desc: A scribe, priest, occasional fraudster, and best friend of Red.

name: Orson
desc: A cavalier of Renais. He’s a devoted husband and a serene and quiet man.

name: Tana
desc: A young lady of Frelia. She is both cheery and sociable.

name: Amelia
desc: A young girl from a small village in Grado. She is honest and sincere.

name: Innes
desc: The prince of Frelia. He’s brash and arrogant, but good at heart.

name: Gerik
desc: A mercenary leader from Jehanna. He's better known as the Desert Tiger.

name: Tethys
desc: A beautiful and charming dancer from Jehanna.

name: Marisa
desc: An aloof sword fighter from Jehanna. She’s known as the Crimson Flash.

name: Mahmoud
desc: A minor noble

name: Mahmoud
desc: A minor noble

name: Mahmoud
desc: Noble but blunt heir of Urgarh

name: Osman
desc: Rightful heir of the entire peninsula. Generous, kind, but naive and idealistic.

name: Saleh
desc: Clever but ruthless heir of Urgarh

name: Amira
desc: An heiress and politician in the local province. Cynical, slightly corrupt, but utterly devoted to peace and improving the land she wishes to rule.
